&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Network topology:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Our cPanel/WHM server is directly connected to a 1Gbps interface with guaranteed bandwidth.  The ISP’s upstream are Magyar Telekom (state telecom), TeliaSonera, Interoute, Deutsche Telekom (via Magyar) and ReTN (as PNI). There are also peering with popular internet exchangers.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;DDoS Filtering:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;
By using custom mitigation devices and the assistance of Magyar Telecom, our infrastructure is protected up to 80Gbps of traffic. DDoS mitigation occurs through a cluster and is permanently activated. It is always self-learning to adapt and understand variations to attack types. We are able to defend against popular attack types such as UDP, spoofed or amplified types, SSYN, TCP, ICMP and any other malformed packets. 
Our solution is independent and does not rely on OVH, Voxility or other common players in the hosting market. This makes us unique.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Payment methods:&lt;/b&gt; We accept PayPal directly, 2CheckOut (for credit or debit cards) or Bitcoin. Our payment accounts are business verified.
